1. *Petak* je najbolji dan u nedelji. (Friday is the best day of the week.)
2. U *petak* uveče je obično najveća gužva. (On Friday night it is usually the busiest.)
3. *Petka* ujutro obično provodim u krevetu. (I usually spend Friday mornings in bed.)
4. Ona je u *petak* popodne otišla u šetnju. (She went for a walk on Friday afternoon.)
5. Da li ćeš doći na zabavu u *petak* veče? (Are you coming to the party on Friday night?)